<section class="section section--tint s4-process">
  <div class="container--narrow">

    <h2 class="s4-process__heading">What To Expect During Your Professional Juvéderm Treatment</h2>
    <p class="s4-process__intro">Every step is designed for your comfort and optimal results. Here's exactly what happens during your treatment at our Millburn practice.</p>

    <ol class="s4-process__list">
      <li class="s4-process__item">
        <strong>Comprehensive Consultation &amp; Assessment (15-20 minutes)</strong>
        <p>Your treatment begins with a detailed facial analysis where our board-certified practitioner evaluates your facial structure, discusses your goals, and creates a customized treatment plan. We'll explain which Juvéderm formulas are best for your specific needs and show you expected results.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="s4-process__item">
        <strong>Preparation &amp; Numbing (10-15 minutes)</strong>
        <p>&#8203;The treatment areas are thoroughly cleansed and marked for precise injection placement. We apply topical numbing cream to ensure your comfort throughout the procedure. The injection sites are carefully planned to achieve natural-looking, balanced results.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="s4-process__item">
        <strong>Precision Juvéderm Injection (20-30 minutes)</strong>
        <p>Using advanced injection techniques, we carefully place the Juvéderm filler in precise locations to achieve your desired results. You'll feel only minimal discomfort due to the numbing cream and Juvéderm's built-in lidocaine. We massage and shape the filler to ensure smooth, even distribution.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="s4-process__item">
        <strong>Post-Treatment Care &amp; Instructions (5-10 minutes)</strong>
        <p>We provide detailed aftercare instructions and schedule your follow-up appointment. You'll receive ice packs to minimize any swelling and specific guidelines to optimize your healing and results. Most clients can return to normal activities immediately.</p>
      </li>
    </ol>

    <h3 class="s4-process__sub-heading">Completely Comfortable &amp; Safe</h3>
    <p class="s4-process__body">Most clients are surprised by how comfortable Juvéderm injections are. The combination of topical numbing and lidocaine in the filler itself minimizes discomfort. The entire process is quicker than most people expect.</p>

  </div>
</section>

